34c3a10d228d23cfce225e0ab34","tid":1262060,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:30:59.000Z","msg":"聽日就G20，聽晚煲底見！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1262072\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1262072</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f571b3efc45e20f2f53a2bea1d1ce204782720ed","tid":1262060,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:33:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"725d774ed8db2ce217da9f6f1eea8b2cffae3c06","tid":1262060,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:34:02.000Z","msg":"[麻煩大家幫手share出去 7月2號就截止申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">已經登記咗都要去查下啲資料啱唔啱</span></strong><br />\n好多人都話冇咗選民記錄 大家都要check下 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/checkvrstatus.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fcheckvrstatus.htm&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPNRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=4d8e04a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/checkvrstatus.htm</a><br />\n或者打電話28911001 &gt; 1 &gt; 2去查 扮工時間9-6<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新登記</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fgcnr.htm&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPNRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=814fc429\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm</a><br />\n電子表格傳送門-&gt; <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C%29.pdf&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPNRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=5dc18eec\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf</a><br />\n實體表格傳送門-&gt; 各區民政事務處<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.had.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcontact_us%2Fcomment_c.htm&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPNRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=8e5744c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm</a><br />\n或公共屋邨辦事處<br />\n<a href=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201901/29/P2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201901%2F29%2FP2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPNRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=2b045055\" target=\"_blank\">http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201901/29/P2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf</a><br />\n或選舉事務處(香港灣仔港灣道25號海港中心10樓/九龍九龍灣展貿徑1號九龍灣國際展貿中心13樓)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">交表</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fvrsubmit.htm&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPNRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=73cbc853\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">如你持有有效的香港郵政或電子核證服務有限公司的電子核證（個人）證書 &lt;- 呢個基本冇人有，所以唔使試</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">免費傳真方法 </span></strong><br />\nHelloFax 免費黑白5張 / FAX.PLUS 免費黑白10張<br />\n<br />\n【教學】選民登記7月2日截止仲未搞？ 教你手機內3分鐘完成手續<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2Fvotersubmit%2Fsoftware%2Fandroid-app%2F&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPNRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=fe136974\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/</a><br />\n<br />\n[/麻煩大家幫手share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]"},{"pid":"cac564c46f0e3d2b3bdb5f9cb595d8e469e0d77b","tid":1262060,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T17:22:52.000Z","msg":"聽日就G20，聽晚煲底見！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1262072\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1262072</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G1fyjv1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG1fyjv1.png&h=98a30dc6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96a5f592f5d69f9ca48ba4addcb0308252b73549","tid":1262060,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T17:24:21.000Z","msg":"去中聯辦喇"},{"pid":"e8b63cf1376dded29adc0a7c45b5dfc4482f43b0","tid":1262060,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cac564c46f0e3d2b3bdb5f9cb595d8e469e0d77b","tid":1262060,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T17:22:52.000Z","msg":"聽日就G20，聽晚煲底見！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1262072\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1262072</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G1fyjv1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG1fyjv1.png&h=98a30dc6&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T17:24:31.000Z","msg":"巴打好熱心"},{"pid":"ed1e959398825527058dc8ddae6d296ce71ddaba","tid":1262060,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8b63cf1376dded29adc0a7c45b5dfc4482f43b0","tid":1262060,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cac564c46f0e3d2b3bdb5f9cb595d8e469e0d77b","tid":1262060,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T17:22:52.000Z","msg":"聽日就G20，聽晚煲底見！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1262072\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1262072</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G1fyjv1.png\"